This is the world's simplest IPN endpoint,
for the OpenHatch donate page.

It does no validation. It just sends emails.

All files in this repo, unless marked otherwise,
are tri-licensed AGPLv3, Apache License 2.0, and
CC Zero.

(C) Asheesh Laroia 2013.


Development setup:

* Create a virtualenv with:

   virtualenv --system-site-packages env

* Install dependencies with:

   env/bin/pip install -r requirements.txt

Now you have to somehow set up the CGI to execute.
